OL,3,CASA bans Huel and Zoe ads over failing
OL,4,Cto disclose links to Steven Bartlett
OL,6,FDragons' Den star Steven Bartlett's
OL,7,Fads for Huel and Zoe have been banned
OL,8,Fby the Advertising Standards Authority
OL,9,F(ASA) for failing to disclose their
OL,10,Fcommercial relationship with the
OL,11,Fcelebrity entrepreneur.
OL,13,FThe ASA found the two adverts for Huel
OL,14,Fand one for Zoe were misleading or
OL,15,Flikely to mislead consumers.
OL,17,FThe ads, seen on Facebook in February,
OL,18,F"omitted material information" about
OL,19,Ftheir links to Bartlett, who is an
OL,20,Finvestor in Zoe and a director at Huel.
