OL,3,CASA bans Huel and Zoe ads over failing
OL,4,Cto disclose links to Steven Bartlett
OL,6,FThe Zoe advert, promoting their offer
OL,7,Fof at-home health tests and a
OL,8,Fpersonalised nutritional programme,
OL,9,Fwas a picture of Bartlett with a Zoe
OL,10,Fpatch on his arm, with a quote from
OL,11,FBartlett saying: "If you haven't tried
OL,12,FZoe yet, give it a shot. It might just
OL,13,Fchange your life."
OL,15,FHuel, who primarily sell meal
OL,16,Freplacement powders, ran ads featuring
OL,17,FBartlett, on the set of his hit
OL,18,Fpodcast The Diary Of A CEO, stating
OL,19,Fthat its Daily Greens powder was the
OL,20,F"best product" it had released.
