OL,3,CASA bans Huel and Zoe ads over failing
OL,4,Cto disclose links to Steven Bartlett
OL,6,FHowever, the ASA found that many
OL,7,Fconsumers were unlikely to understand
OL,8,Ffrom the ads that Bartlett had a
OL,9,Ffinancial interest in the companies'
OL,10,Fperformance.
OL,12,FOn Zoe, the regulator said: "Steven
OL,13,FBartlett was an investor in Zoe, which
OL,14,Fwe considered was material to
OL,15,Fconsumers' understanding of the ad and
OL,16,Frelevant in making an informed
OL,17,Fdecision about the product.
