OL,3,CASA bans Huel and Zoe ads over failing
OL,4,Cto disclose links to Steven Bartlett
OL,6,F"Because the ad omitted material
OL,7,Finformation about Steven Bartlett
OL,8,Fbeing an investor in Zoe, we concluded
OL,9,Fthat it was misleading."
OL,11,FIn regards to Huel: "We considered
OL,12,Fthat Bartlett's directorship was
OL,13,Fmaterial to consumers' understanding
OL,14,Fof the ads, and so relevant for them
OL,15,Fin making an informed decision about
OL,16,Fthe advertised product.
OL,18,F"Because the ads omitted material
OL,19,Finformation about Steven Bartlett's
OL,20,Fposition as a director at Huel, we
OL,21,Fconcluded they were likely to mislead."
